        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Ensuring VA Employee Accountability Act</strong></p> <p>Requires the Department of Veterans Affairs (VA) to retain a copy of any reprimand or admonishment received by a VA employee in the employee's permanent record.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
      <summary>
