        <actionDate>2015-05-18</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Passed House without amendment</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2015-05-19T20:52:16Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>(This measure has not been amended since it was introduced. The summary has been expanded because action occurred on the measure.)</p> <p><strong>Ensuring VA Employee Accountability Act</strong></p> <p>(Sec. 2) Requires the Department of Veterans Affairs (VA) to retain a copy of any reprimand or admonishment received by a VA employee in the employee's permanent record.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
